      • reversed

        public IndexedEdge reversed()
                     throws RebarException
        Return a reversed view of this edge (where src and dst are swapped). I.e., if this IndexedEdge's direction is V1_TO_V2, then return a new IndexedEdge for the same edge but with direction V2_TO_V1; and vice versa.
        Throws:
        RebarException
